<div type="abstract"><head>Offener Brief des Rates</head><p>Der Rat bevollmächtigt Burkhard Hofner und Hans Stetzman, Diener der Stadt, zur Vertretung vor dem Landgericht zu Hirschberg wegen der Klage von Margarethe Drahtschmied aus Ingolstadt um Güter.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_207_line_1585991750612_372">Wir ~ etc <expan>Bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc / Vmb ſölıch ladung vnd klage als Margret </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l6">die drotſmidin 
<add><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l5">von Jngelſtat </ab></add> tut auf <expan>vnſe<ex>r</ex></expan> gute in der lantſchrann cʒu <expan>hirſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l7">gelegen / daʒ vvir darümb <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> hofner vnd hanſen Stecʒman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l8"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd vollen gevvalt / das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l9">von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> Stat cʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antvvurten</expan> vnd cʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>trete<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_207_r1l11">cʒu gevvẏnne vnd cʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>luſte</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_207_r1l10">vnd cʒu <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab></add> Mit <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_207" id="103r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir etc. <expan>bek<ex>ennen</ex></expan> etc. umb sölich ladung und klage,
                        als Margret die Drotsmidin <add>von Ingelstat</add> tut auf
                                <expan>unse<ex>r</ex></expan> gute in der lantschrann czu
                                <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> gelegen, daz wir darümb
                                <expan>Burkh<ex>art</ex></expan> Hofner und Hansen Steczman,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> dienern,
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> und vollen gewalt, das von
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> und an <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> stat czu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antwurten</expan> und czu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>trete<ex>n</ex></expan>, czu gewynne und czu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>luste</expan>
<add>und czu <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>recht<ex>en</ex></expan></add>. Mit
                            <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
